## HTTP API

Public request and response structs live in `api/http/model/`. Define complex Go structs there, then add and generate operations with:

```bash
jgo api add OperationName --method GET --path /rpc_style_path \
  --request name:type:required:query \
  --response-data ResponseStruct
jgo api generate
jgo list
```
{{end}}
